      "para_id": "Q001656.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Ninmarki , the kind woman , the firstborn child of Nanše , Šulgi , the powerful man , king of Urim , king of Sumer and Akkad , built her E-munus-gisa ."
    }
